Title: Effective potential in Brane-World scenarios

Authors: Oriol Pujolas

Comments: 11 pages, 1 figure. To appear in the proceedings of the 5th Peyresq

meeting. References and notes addedJournal-ref: Int.J.Theor.Phys. 40 (2001) 2131-2142

We review the stabilization of the radion in the Randall-Sundrum modelthrough the Casimir energy due to a bulk conformally coupled field. We alsoshow some exact self-consistent solutions taking into account the backreactionthat this energy induces on the geometry.